{"tid":81603,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]睇波歐洲之旅","createTime":"2017-01-15T12:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T01:33:44.000Z","uid":61170,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a8458b295bc7101638e9bdd0fbe1c5bc27146a9","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"唔知仲有冇巴絲記得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係好耐之前出咗篇遊記係歐洲睇波之旅<br />\n因為係隔離台出post<br />\n加上之前英國行程係睇完阿仙奴場波就完<br />\n咁我之後有時間再係呢度補返post啦<br />\n講返個旅程,<br />\n成個trip總共去咗5個地方,包括英國,直布羅陀,法國,西班牙同埋莫斯科<br />\n其實都成年前去,<br />\n因為今年真係太忙,<br />\n係出咗英國篇之後就停咗,<br />\n直到而家有返少少時間就出返post<br />\n真係要同咁多位巴絲講返句唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n補返少少阿記場波啲相俾各位睇下先<br />\n一年前,住烏仲係正選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/irmdp94s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Firmdp94s&h=3678a026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sfpzgo6n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsfpzgo6n&h=c0c70e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sf9hi7kp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsf9hi7kp&h=4ccf5757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瀟灑的奧燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pbshrcfg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpbshrcfg&h=50e231f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4qeuj75c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4qeuj75c&h=f171c474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sb81x567\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsb81x567&h=5217560c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3rtbhf8j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3rtbhf8j&h=2b6d45b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4lzk36ti\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4lzk36ti&h=4e568ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1v9o6nz3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1v9o6nz3&h=c5bdf608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mqzxi94v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmqzxi94v&h=4bbb4a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w0c31k8h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw0c31k8h&h=26445395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nr9628ft\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnr9628ft&h=e0324283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0c8qgh79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0c8qgh79&h=27db29bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jwu52m1e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjwu52m1e&h=3e3eb7d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a60fa29dca7d021722fbdd44b4494f5dd8c83e6","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"係埸波完咗之後個日,<br />\n我就離開London去直布羅陀<br />\n介紹返少少先,<br />\n直布羅陀係英國其中一個殖民地,<br />\n位於西班牙南部La Linea再落<br />\n成個直布羅陀人口4萬至5萬人<br />\n與惜日的香港同樣係英國的殖民地,<br />\n但命運卻不同,<br />\n人嘅質素比香港更高,更團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出發前當然要煮返餐靚早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係買得太多要食晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fehu5oxg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffehu5oxg&h=14e87e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCheck 完in就準備入air side啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yvtqjc2e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyvtqjc2e&h=31d41a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行下免稅店<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ws0ik5h3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fws0ik5h3&h=49cee59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ta4i8jog\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fta4i8jog&h=b7318ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前面就係GATE啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sv8fi2ma\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsv8fi2ma&h=5eb88427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咦?啲人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5fyxg306\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5fyxg306&h=ea0976a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩啲人只係落咗去下一層,嚇得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rlvmcz3w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frlvmcz3w&h=51aa20a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日係搭British Airways BA490去直布羅陀<br />\n機型係A320<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vblrtgp2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvblrtgp2&h=cd67b169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上機啦!不過唔係行機橋,係行去機尾上樓梯<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8i2wpd3b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8i2wpd3b&h=e54c9771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8mq5il7e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8mq5il7e&h=16420850&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"784faa1855be383c073cb23be3e13b979da06f37","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:33:08.000Z","msg":"VA 787係隔離行過<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cm2g8soa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcm2g8soa&h=4de2d859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8kzpmjr2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8kzpmjr2&h=1cab0d6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上到機坐低,發覺窗中間有隻嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fbtvw69e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffbtvw69e&h=05c057dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解見到國泰就有啲親切嘅感覺<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l8mnkjbi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl8mnkjbi&h=3843b838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話咁快就起飛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jwv1hzge\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjwv1hzge&h=addc3b5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要咗呢隻酒飲,味道一般<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zikd078a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzikd078a&h=ecd96765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就快降落啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8mc324v0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8mc324v0&h=0a54d29e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為直布羅陀機場跑道嘅設計同地形關係,飛機降落咗之後要去到跑道尾backtrack,再沿住條跑道taxi返去parking bay<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q83f17po\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq83f17po&h=3caa864b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k7puos3b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk7puos3b&h=9ec96857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢架船就係我今晚book咗嘅酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9mnz8dkw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9mnz8dkw&h=3a0a57c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAIR FORCE的base就在terminal對面<br />\n來自ROYAL AIRFORCE 的AIRBUS A400M<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m0fpsauz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm0fpsauz&h=afe40b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落機了,要行去Terminal做入境手續<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jdsgq8uv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjdsgq8uv&h=50c1f052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由入境大樓望返去停機坪都只係一路之隔<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e2zov3yp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe2zov3yp&h=478e23e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n排隊入passport control<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iw9e2s61\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fiw9e2s61&h=05cff50a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPassport control有兩個counters<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zqjwi19d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzqjwi19d&h=57451209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於拎得行李<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/43vaq1y9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F43vaq1y9&h=8cb1232b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWelcome to GIBRALTAR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0erdcvil\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0erdcvil&h=e34126ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b440f86f640081c52e638ed5a2f3ed4ee0c34826","tid":81603,"uid":12241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:34:08.000Z","msg":"留名睇人旅行<br />\n加油比多D圖"},{"pid":"ed823dbe8aaf53f0249ce3fe86fd15108219c121","tid":81603,"uid":22277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"評已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好似認得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b69633d30ee705281f499ea2e7cbdf0e151c5b","tid":81603,"uid":21628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e0dbcefb3c5cd9e58b13b3c52c1bfb9ac02f74fa","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:40:00.000Z","msg":"而家食嘢先<br />\n陣間再出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9d42ebd0c4095662b4553a9bb8da2ea564ee97","tid":81603,"uid":2093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"點買波飛?"},{"pid":"4e4fcf22ad93855027ef73069b26ceb259bbf777","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"一踏出機埸就搵路去酒店先,因為近機埸,所以決定行過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gcbjxi35\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgcbjxi35&h=556f2174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機埸隔離就係陸路關口行過去西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tjpy976b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftjpy976b&h=a4ae5b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人,車,飛機共用的道路<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ufo8e7kd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fufo8e7kd&h=e8cffc92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有飛機起飛降落就要暫時封閉<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yh6jpfgq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyh6jpfgq&h=65ed7fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n起飛了,BYEBYE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j7k45qod\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj7k45qod&h=8600c3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當飛機起飛後就可以過對面啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zb3x0ngs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzb3x0ngs&h=9d75c5a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dp1j4fzt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdp1j4fzt&h=4f7da895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bolt8ugr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbolt8ugr&h=64b82b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xqnphacr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxqnphacr&h=f5282fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ymtkbspl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fymtkbspl&h=6ce345a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有架fighter<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2zx0wtgu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2zx0wtgu&h=65b28d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yg0pz2vk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyg0pz2vk&h=5bcc6c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿路見到啲屋邨樓下有個公園,有小朋友係度玩<br />\n個感覺真係幾似香港啲公共屋邨<br />\n不過少咗啲蝗味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/59e7vadu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F59e7vadu&h=dc826a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mtedurzs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmtedurzs&h=e00332db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad60b23a33f55637a93b697491e1093b07937c2a","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點買波飛?</blockquote><br />\n巴打你想問英超定西甲?"},{"pid":"5157836401f5e10fbdefd1593650401f2bff7b3c","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:40:58.000Z","msg":"跟著因為行錯路<br />\n向一位姐姐問路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲好人到親自帶我到酒店門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n非常之友善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實在太好人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾經波折,終於去到酒店門口(碼頭)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1txghv0p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1txghv0p&h=dcc98fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dzh0ef2v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdzh0ef2v&h=0560197f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0agknho9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0agknho9&h=fe459b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個大堂真係幾靚,仲有杯Champagne做Welcome drink<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lqe1vcxw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flqe1vcxw&h=d6a2d469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ora0n8s7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fora0n8s7&h=eb8d1b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5iwvykb9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5iwvykb9&h=0bc6057e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於可以上房啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ujqf5e4g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fujqf5e4g&h=1c38d3b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間房有個露台,好靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sy9bjk5r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsy9bjk5r&h=6c24faca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個景都唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2k4e7yfb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2k4e7yfb&h=80854a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上咗甲板睇日落,地下藍色燈個度就係跑道<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ow968bt0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fow968bt0&h=c0a62950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚啲燈光真係好靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9fesh02m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9fesh02m&h=e19d90d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d72bcbdee02004b18f4d4014a96f06ee59466ec","tid":81603,"uid":49266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點買波飛?</blockquote><br />\n巴打你想問英超定西甲?</blockquote><br />\nwhy not both"},{"pid":"780ebe252e00ee91920a7ec025c5ffe04c60ccff","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點買波飛?</blockquote><br />\n巴打你想問英超定西甲?</blockquote><br />\nwhy not both</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英超係搵當地一個朋友買<br />\n入場時用卡拍卡入<br />\n<br />\n而西甲，我就係viagogo買<br />\n臨開波前係班拿貝附近一間酒店拎ticket<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b2aa571b91eb7ae3aec9d0f2c7d68fff888508","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T15:28:06.000Z","msg":"到第二日,一起身就發覺個天陰陰地<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/y1n8b5iz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fy1n8b5iz&h=ec0f0b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oti3le69\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foti3le69&h=848764fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出發去join一個local tour,<br />\n全車得個導遊,一對英國夫婦同埋我<br />\n第一個景點係睇呢啲屋,呢啲屋係比老人家養老嘅<br />\n個景非常正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有段小插曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n導遊比我地落車行下影下相,咁我當然好興奮咁落車啦<br />\n不幸嘅事件就發生了,因為附近比較多馬騮<br />\n一落車就踩咗舊馬騮屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個導遊好nice咁叫我係草地度刮走啲屎,<br />\n但我見到佢係度偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sle2k0i3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsle2k0i3&h=72961fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ztqr0dw4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fztqr0dw4&h=11d9d72f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mktuzlyr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmktuzlyr&h=0d84818e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6l8fpxbw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6l8fpxbw&h=628c4f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地架「旅遊巴」<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6wvq5p4r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6wvq5p4r&h=a701c77c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地陣間就會上個巨石上邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mtsn9gro\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmtsn9gro&h=54163a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同行對夫婦好開心咁影相<br />\n我就好撚努力咁刮走啲屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4c9bfa71651f0210eda3f82e281bb620b0a363","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"過咗十五分鍾,<br />\n導遊叫返我地上車準備去下一個景點<br />\n屌,開咗車之後仲聞到陣臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲諗係咪同行對夫婦放屁<br />\n但醒起自己對鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再見到個導遊較低個車窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到下一個景點<br />\n個景點有個紀念碑係度,好似係紀念若干年前戰爭時的英雄(隔咗成年唔係好記得個導遊講乜)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hlbx93rd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhlbx93rd&h=5049f40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個風景真係好靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1w5cvxeu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1w5cvxeu&h=56afe820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a87elh9o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa87elh9o&h=ab061c02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b092003e1fe57f597b96a5939eae52e6684a3e4","tid":81603,"uid":61170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T15:33:14.000Z","msg":"跟著就去咗睇鐘乳石<br />\n一去到,真係好多馬騮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個遊客特登拎啲膠袋引佢地搶<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kcip6fm9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkcip6fm9&h=18cc726e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知隻馬騮一打開<br />\n「屌你空盒黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n個樣即刻頹撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r01cg3ix\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr01cg3ix&h=ab238212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/67rgtew9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F67rgtew9&h=3ca2b93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p8yuwc34\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp8yuwc34&h=f7374642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kd7roixw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkd7roixw&h=9675ddc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tdj8wbsm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftdj8wbsm&h=e6b9314a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0dz9q3s6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0dz9q3s6&h=584c7f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話咁快就睇完出返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x5f4hbgc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx5f4hbgc&h=efc702f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越上得高就越多馬騮,好多一家大細出黎搵食<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fzo8l1k2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffzo8l1k2&h=4feec98e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係太記得條tunnel係打仗個陣有咩用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6dlcv7fw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6dlcv7fw&h=7e5b3a87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟著再行到去一座堡壘<br />\n以前係用黎困住啲戰俘<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ctl3ijpn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fctl3ijpn&h=e60db4f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l26shqid\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl26shqid&h=e59bd2a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9ogqif6u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9ogqif6u&h=6dd6ad08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zlgs1vtq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzlgs1vtq&h=35d357ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yps18tlx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyps18tlx&h=fefff136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返到酒店,見仲有啲時間<br />\n於是就行去西班牙食個下午茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行咗大約15分鍾就黎到關口<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/56ni2tp4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F56ni2tp4&h=bae782e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度就係個關口入口<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4roi9cuk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4roi9cuk&h=bc1918e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係用BNO,所以過關可以去e道,scan一下就過得,既方便又快捷<br />\n但用特區護照嘅朋友就要排隊過人手櫃台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76dce7c8d504fdd59f19ac722b440e22908bc05","tid":81603,"uid":22277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"嘩，咁快出咗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名陣間扮工睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}